snippet.title: Mother of Australian boy raises awareness of bullying in viral video
snippet.description:
An Australian mother has given a heartbreaking account of the devastating effects bullying can have on children. In a video that has attracted an outpouring of support, 9-year-old son Quaden Bayles, who has dwarfism, cries that he wants to kill himself after being taunted by a classmate over his height.

Full story: https://cna.asia/2SL6XYf

(Video: Yarraka Bayles)
